p414
aVThe long-lasting damage of nuclear radiation
p415
aVcaused an entire city and its population
p416
aVto turn into powder.
p417
aVWhen I was born, my mom says I looked around the whole hospital room
p418
aVwith a stare that said, "This? I've done this before."
p419
aVShe says I have old eyes.
p420
aVWhen my Grandpa Genji died, I was only five years old,
p421
aVbut I took my mom by the hand and told her,
p422
aV"Don't worry, he'll come back as a baby."
